comment._content: Hello, this is the blind astrometry solver. Your results are: I'm sorry to say that I couldn't solve your system. However there is some good news! Someone should be around soon to solve your image by applying a few tweaks. We'll let you know how that goes. ----- If you would like to have other images solved, please submit them to the astrometry group.
